data.description: Great opportunity investment property in hot Austin community! Three Flat Apartment Building sitting on double lot (629 & 631 N Laramie). Both lots being sold together and reflected in list price. The open lot (629 N Laramie) makes for a great side yard and play space. Lot next door includes an additional two-car garage which offers additional rental income and parking. Forced air furnaces with duct work. There are separate laundry hookups and circuit breaker panels for each floor.  Full unfinished basement with good ceiling height has great potential. 6 total bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Unique opportunity as owner-occupied or investment property. Property is being sold AS IS.
